data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom/ 3.5 bathroom newer home on over an acre just under 15 minutes to Target, Publix, restaurants, and more! Dockside Cove is a very quiet gated lake community with stunning custom homes on estate lots in a private wooded lake setting. This home sits beautifully atop the lot for an elevated view! You are greeted with high-quality interior finishes, gleaming hardwood floors, extensive trim detail, and the openness of the floor plan is filled with incredible natural light with exposed beams in the oversized living room with a marble surround on the wood burning fireplace, and an incredible open concept, ideal for entertaining or enjoying the private wooded and nature views with the abundance of windows! Head into the open concept gourmet kitchen with gorgeous quartz countertops, generous oversized island, beautiful white cabinets, with ample cabinet/ counter space, and state of the art stainless steel kitchenaid appliances! Breathtaking walk in custom pantry, could be used as an additional prep space with incredible storage! Oversized laundry room with beautiful views, ample counter space, sink, and custom cabinetry. Grand primary suite on the main with views to the backyard with access to the covered patio! Luxurious primary bath is absolutely breathtaking with a beautiful freestanding soaking tub, stunning frameless glass shower with overhead rainfall shower in addition to the whole body shower head. Large custom primary closet with amazing natural light! Head upstairs to the second primary suite with incredible natural light, gorgeous ensuite with frameless glass shower and spacious vanity, and oversized walk-in closet! Additional bonus space that could be used as an additional bedroom, media room, office, etc! Two additional generous sized bedrooms on the second level with ample closet space just down the hall. Huge additional attic space, perfect for extra storage! Enjoy the grand private backyard with a beautiful fire pit, hot tub, and covered patio- plumbed for an outdoor kitchen, ideal for entertaining! Spacious 3 car garage with custom barndoor separating the 3rd stall, perfect for a man cave/ workshop! This gorgeous community has a community dock with 2 available boat slips by separate owners, both slips are uncovered and deep water! **Assumable mortgage with low interest rate of 4.5%!! Reach out for more information!! **
